    <title><![CDATA[Apache + Php Config On Yosemite]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.tiny1024.com/2015/07/09/Apache-Php-Config-On-Yosemite/"/>
    <id>http://www.tiny1024.com/2015/07/09/Apache-Php-Config-On-Yosemite/</id>
    <published>2015-07-09T06:04:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-07-09T06:24:24.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="启用_php">启用 php</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo vi /etc/apache2/httpd.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>取消下面一行的注释：<br><figure class="highlight gradle"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="regexp">/LoadModule php5_module libexec/</span>apache2<span class="regexp">/libphp5.so</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="启用每个用户的支持">启用每个用户的支持</h2><p>启用之后就可以使用<a href="http://localhost/~username/来访问每个用户自己的网站" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost/~username/来访问每个用户自己的网站</a><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo mkdir ~/Sites/</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo vi /etc/apache2/users/michael.conf</span><br><span class="line">&lt;pre&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;Directory <span class="string">"/Users/michael/Sites/"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    Options Indexes MultiViews</span><br><span class="line">    AllowOverride None</span><br><span class="line">    Require all granted</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/Directory&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/pre&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo chmod <span class="number">775</span> /etc/apache2/users/michael.conf</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo vi /etc/apache2/httpd.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;pre&gt;</span><br><span class="line">LoadModule authz_core_module libexec/apache2/mod_authz_core.so</span><br><span class="line">LoadModule authz_host_module libexec/apache2/mod_authz_host.so</span><br><span class="line">LoadModule userdir_module libexec/apache2/mod_userdir.so</span><br><span class="line">Include /private/etc/apache2/extra/httpd-userdir.conf</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/pre&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo vi /etc/apache2/extra/httpd-userdir.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;pre&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Include /private/etc/apache2/users/*.conf</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/pre&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Restart_apache">Restart apache</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apachectl restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
